msg: In the status walker: Only check for svn:externals properties on directories
that we know have properties. (This reduces the status time with about 3%

we know the directory has properties. Update caller.
(make_dir_baton): Don't assume checking text_mods. Pass TRUE for had props.
(svn_wc_get_status_editor5): Use pcalloc and set new value in baton.
